                            <comment id="15182131" author="gagravarr" created="Sun, 6 Mar 2016 12:34:19 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;With your patch applied, the Tika app correctly detects your new text file for me, both with and without the filename hint:&lt;/p&gt;
